{
  "code": 200,
  "status": "OK",
  "data": {
    "number": 54,
    "name": "سُورَةُ القَمَرِ",
    "englishName": "Al-Qamar",
    "englishNameTranslation": "The Moon",
    "revelationType": "Meccan",
    "numberOfAyahs": 55,
    "ayahs": [
      {
        "number": 4847,
        "text": "复活的时间临近了，月亮破裂了[注]。",
        "numberInSurah": 1,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4848,
        "text": "假如他们看见一种迹象，他们就避开，并且说：“这是一种常表演的魔术。”",
        "numberInSurah": 2,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4849,
        "text": "他们否认[《古兰经》]，顺从自己的私欲。每件事都会有个定论[行善者入乐园，作恶者入火狱]。",
        "numberInSurah": 3,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4850,
        "text": "[《古兰经》中]许多包含警戒的消息确已降临他们，",
        "numberInSurah": 4,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4851,
        "text": "那是完美的智慧[《古兰经》]，但[仅凭]警告者[对他们的宣教]是无益[不够]的。",
        "numberInSurah": 5,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4852,
        "text": "所以，你[穆圣]当避开他们。当召唤者召唤[他们]至可怕之事的那日[复活日]，",
        "numberInSurah": 6,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4853,
        "text": "他们将目光卑贱地从坟墓中出来，好像四散的蝗虫，",
        "numberInSurah": 7,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4854,
        "text": "急忙奔向召唤者。不信仰者将说：“这是一个苦难的日子。”",
        "numberInSurah": 8,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4855,
        "text": "在他们之前，努哈的族人曾否认[过他们的使者]。他们否认我的仆人说：“他是个疯子。”他曾受非难[和威胁]。",
        "numberInSurah": 9,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4856,
        "text": "所以他祈求他的主[说]：“我失败了，求你襄助我吧！”",
        "numberInSurah": 10,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4857,
        "text": "因此，我打开了天门，降下倾盆大雨，",
        "numberInSurah": 11,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4858,
        "text": "并使大地涌出泉水。[雨]水[和泉水]奉既定的命令汇合。",
        "numberInSurah": 12,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4859,
        "text": "我使他[努哈]乘坐在一只用木板和钉子制造的船上，",
        "numberInSurah": 13,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4860,
        "text": "那艘船在我的眷顾之下航行[飘游]，以报酬被人否认者。",
        "numberInSurah": 14,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4861,
        "text": "我确已把此事[努哈圣人的船和洪水]留作一种迹象，但有接受劝告的人吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 15,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4862,
        "text": "我的刑罚和警告多可怕！",
        "numberInSurah": 16,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4863,
        "text": "我确已使《古兰经》容易记诵[注]，但有接受劝告的人吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 17,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4864,
        "text": "阿德人曾否认[过他们的使者胡德]。我的刑罚和警告多可怕！",
        "numberInSurah": 18,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4865,
        "text": "我确已派遣刺耳的狂风在一个苦难不幸之日惩罚他们。",
        "numberInSurah": 19,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4866,
        "text": "那狂风将人们拔[吹]起，他们好像被连根拔起的椰枣树干一样。",
        "numberInSurah": 20,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4867,
        "text": "我的刑罚和警告多可怕！",
        "numberInSurah": 21,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4868,
        "text": "我确已使《古兰经》容易记诵，但有接受劝告的人吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 22,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4869,
        "text": "萨姆德人曾否认警告。",
        "numberInSurah": 23,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4870,
        "text": "他们说：“[他只是]我们同族的一个凡人，难道我们能追随他[萨利哈圣人]吗？如果这样，我们必陷于迷误和疯狂中。",
        "numberInSurah": 24,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4871,
        "text": "在我们这些人中，难道启示只降给他[萨利哈圣人]一人吗？不，他是说谎者，是傲慢者。”",
        "numberInSurah": 25,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4872,
        "text": "他们明天将知道谁是说谎者，谁是傲慢者。",
        "numberInSurah": 26,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4873,
        "text": "我必将派一头母驼[注]考验他们，所以你[萨利哈圣人]当监视他们，当忍耐。",
        "numberInSurah": 27,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4874,
        "text": "你当告诉他们，[井]水是他们[人与母驼]所共享的，每个都有权轮流饮水。",
        "numberInSurah": 28,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4875,
        "text": "但他们叫来了他们的同伴，他[他们的同伴]拿起剑把母驼杀了。",
        "numberInSurah": 29,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4876,
        "text": "我的刑罚和警告多可怕！",
        "numberInSurah": 30,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4877,
        "text": "我确已派遣恐怖声[注]惩罚他们，他们变成了好像建羊圈者用剩的残梗一样。",
        "numberInSurah": 31,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4878,
        "text": "我确已使《古兰经》容易记诵，但有接受劝告的人吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 32,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4879,
        "text": "鲁特的族人曾否认警告。",
        "numberInSurah": 33,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4880,
        "text": "我确已派遣飞砂走石的暴风惩罚他们，唯鲁特的家人例外，我在天亮前拯救了他们。",
        "numberInSurah": 34,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4881,
        "text": "那是从我降示的恩惠，我如此报酬感恩者。",
        "numberInSurah": 35,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4882,
        "text": "他[鲁特]确已把我的刑罚警告他们，但他们怀疑警告。",
        "numberInSurah": 36,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4883,
        "text": "他们确已企图让他在他的客人面前丢脸[如邀请他的客人与他们一起搞同性恋]，所以我使他们的眼看不见。[我说]：“你们尝试我的刑罚和警告吧！”",
        "numberInSurah": 37,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4884,
        "text": "一种永久的刑罚确已在清晨袭击他们。",
        "numberInSurah": 38,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4885,
        "text": "[我说]：“你们尝试我的刑罚和警告吧！”",
        "numberInSurah": 39,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4886,
        "text": "我确已使《古兰经》容易记诵，但有接受劝告的人吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 40,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4887,
        "text": "警告[通过穆萨和哈伦]确已降临法老的人民，",
        "numberInSurah": 41,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4888,
        "text": "但他们否认我的所有迹象，因而我以全能的、万能的主的刑罚惩治了他们。",
        "numberInSurah": 42,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4889,
        "text": "[古莱什人啊！]你们中的不信仰者比这些人[如努哈的族人，鲁特的族人，萨利哈的族人和法老的人民等]更好呢？还是天经中有对你们的赦免？",
        "numberInSurah": 43,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4890,
        "text": "难道他们要说“他们是一个常胜的团体”吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 44,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4891,
        "text": "那个团体将被击溃，他们将败北而逃。",
        "numberInSurah": 45,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4892,
        "text": "不，复活的时间是他们的约期，复活的时间是最艰难的，是最痛苦的。",
        "numberInSurah": 46,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4893,
        "text": "犯罪者[今世]的确在迷误中，[后世]的确在[火狱的]烧灼中。",
        "numberInSurah": 47,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4894,
        "text": "他们趴着被拖入火狱的那日，[有话声对他们说]：“你们尝试火狱的烧灼吧！”",
        "numberInSurah": 48,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4895,
        "text": "我的确依前定[或定量]创造万物。",
        "numberInSurah": 49,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4896,
        "text": "我的命令只有一个，犹如转眼之间。",
        "numberInSurah": 50,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 531,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4897,
        "text": "我确已毁灭了你们的宗派，但有接受劝告的人吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 51,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 531,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4898,
        "text": "凡是他们所做的，都已记录在功过簿中。",
        "numberInSurah": 52,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 531,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4899,
        "text": "无论小事大事，都已被记录[注]。",
        "numberInSurah": 53,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 531,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4900,
        "text": "敬畏者必在乐园和有河流的地方。",
        "numberInSurah": 54,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 531,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4901,
        "text": "在万能的主那里，必有一个如意的席位[永居乐园]。",
        "numberInSurah": 55,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 531,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      }
    ],
